                                                 BUSINESS QUESTION
           What % of users have: 
o	sleep < 6 hours 
o	anxiety > 7 

                       QUERY
SELECT
ROUND(100.0 * SUM(CASE WHEN sleep_hours < 6 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / COUNT(*),2) AS percentage_low_sleep,
ROUND(100.0 * SUM(CASE WHEN anxiety_level > 7 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / COUNT(*),2) AS percentage_high_anxiety
FROM mental_health;

INSIGHT
From this query a meaningful portion of users are sleep-deprived and highly anxious.
